OL,3,CHow badly has your water supplier
OL,4,Cranked in damning new pollution report?
OL,6,FThe number of serious pollution
OL,7,Fincidents caused by water firms across
OL,8,FEngland increased by 60% in 2024
OL,9,Fcompared to the previous year, a
OL,10,Fdamning new report shows.
OL,12,FAll nine water and sewage firms in the
OL,13,Fcountry showed consistently poor
OL,14,Fperformance, the Environment Agency
OL,15,F(EA) said, despite expectations that
OL,16,Fincidents would decrease.
