OL,3,CHow badly has your water supplier
OL,4,Cranked in damning new pollution report?
OL,6,FThree water firms were responsible for
OL,7,F81% of these serious incidents `
OL,8,FThames Water with 33, Southern Water
OL,9,Fwith 15 and Yorkshire Water with 13,
OL,10,Fthe watchdog's report found.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, just two companies `
OL,13,FNorthumbrian Water and Wessex Water `
OL,14,Fhad no serious incidents last year,
OL,15,Fmeeting the EA's expectations to see a
OL,16,Ftrend to zero pollution incidents by
OL,17,F2025.
