OL,3,CHow badly has your water supplier
OL,4,Cranked in damning new pollution report?
OL,6,FOverall, the watchdog said all
OL,7,Fpollution incidents across England's
OL,8,Fnine suppliers, including category 1
OL,9,F(major), category 2 (significant) and
OL,10,Fcategory 3 (minor) incidents,
OL,11,Fincreased by 29%, to 2,801, up from
OL,12,F2,174 in 2023.
OL,14,FAn increasing trend in pollution
OL,15,Fspills from pipes carrying wastewater
OL,16,Fuphill emerged last year, accounting
OL,17,Ffor 20% of the serious incidents, the
OL,18,FEnvironment Agency said, adding that
OL,19,Fthese affected some protected waters
OL,20,Ffor wildlife and swimming.
