OL,3,CHow badly has your water supplier
OL,4,Cranked in damning new pollution report?
OL,6,FThe report comes before the
OL,7,Fpublication of a landmark review of
OL,8,Fthe water industry on Monday, led by
OL,9,FSir John Cunliffe, who will outline
OL,10,Fhis recommendations to the Government
OL,11,Fon tackling the sector's performance.
OL,13,FIt also follows a report released by
OL,14,Fthe Public Accounts Committee earlier
OL,15,Fon Friday, in which the cross-bench
OL,16,Fgroup of MPs called the level of
OL,17,Fpollution "woeful" and called for an
OL,18,Foverhaul of the regulation system.
