OL,6,FEA chairman Alan Lovell said: "This
OL,7,Freport demonstrates continued systemic
OL,8,Ffailure by some companies to meet
OL,9,Ftheir environmental targets.
OL,11,F"The water industry must act urgently
OL,12,Fto prevent pollution from occurring
OL,13,Fand to respond rapidly when it does.
OL,15,F"We have made significant changes to
OL,16,Ftighten our regulation of the water
OL,17,Findustry and ensure companies are held
OL,18,Fto account."
