OL,3,CHow badly has your water supplier
OL,4,Cranked in damning new pollution report?
OL,6,FOn the Environment Agency's report
OL,7,Freleased today, River Action's chief
OL,8,Fexecutive James Wallace said the
OL,9,Ffigures "expose a brutal truth".
OL,11,F"Serious pollution incidents are
OL,12,Frising, sewage discharges remain
OL,13,Frampant, and our rivers are spiralling
OL,14,Ftoward ecological collapse," he said,
OL,15,Fcalling for the "most egregious
OL,16,Fpolluter" Thames Water to be put into
OL,17,Fspecial administration.
OL,19,F"This is not just regulatory failure;
OL,20,Fit is a national disgrace."
